Title: Nagios: Log external commands to nagios.log by default
Level: 1
Component: core
Compatible: compat
Edition: cre
Version: 1.5.0i1
Date: 1507887368
Class: fix

Nagios is now logging external commands to the core log (nagios.log)
in the default configuration. This makes Nagios behave like the Microcore
in this case.
